items.sentence: I don't think Tom knows who gave me this umbrella.

Our city is rather small in comparison with Tokyo.
Stock prices were mixed on the Tokyo market today.
The Mitsubishi Bank merged with the Bank of Tokyo.
I can't afford to rent a house like this in Tokyo.
My brother soon got used to living alone in Tokyo.
I'm the one who broke the windshield of Tom's car.
You should've known better than to lend Tom money.
Several people drowned, but many made it to shore.
